126=     A  I don't have a home telephone any longer
fmt=pb
127=  just a cell phone that number is 555-1212.
128=     Q  What's your job title now?
129=     A  Manufacturing Director.
130=     Q  How long has that been your job title?
131=     A  Since spring of '99.
132=     Q  How long have you been there?
133=     A  How long?   
