374=     Q   Exhibit 9 for the deposition of Sam 
375= Parker is a document titled Memo - Performance
376= Improvement Program, and this memo is directed
fmt=pb
377=  to Gil Bower, correct?
378=     A   Yes.
379=     Q   Isn't it true that on June 15th, 2006,
