433= present besides you and Gil Bower in your office
434= on June 15, 2006 at the meeting in which you told
435= Mr. Bower he had three chances to sign the 
436= performance improvement plan?
437=     A   Yes.
438=     Q   Who else was present?
439=     A   I asked Cynthia Roth to step into my office
440= to act as a witness to the discussion.
441=     Q   What was the purpose of having a witness
442= present?
443=     A   I felt that since Gil was not going to sign
444= the improvement plan then I would have to recommend
445= his termination and I did not want there to be any 
446= question as to what exactly I told him. So far there
447= seem to be entirely too many questions on a subject
448= which too me does not seem complicated.
449=     Q   Was it also your intent to have Ms. Roth
450= witness your termination of Mr. Bower?
451=     MR. MCAVOY:  Objection, asked and answered.
