464= a witness to the statements we were making. If 
465= you are in any way implying that Cynthia is in
466= some way biased against Gil, I do not believe 
467= that is true. After her years of excellent 
468= service to DC Corp she may be now have some 
469= understandable loyalty to her employer, but that
470= is perfectly natural and understandlable.
